      "content": "there isnt really any pain though, just that weird muffled feeling. i'm a bit scared to go to the doctor and have them poke around in there if it's just wax. do you think the hydrogen peroxide will definitely fix it? i'd rather just try that at home first if it's just a minor thing like you said.",
